name: sita_Line mix
description:
summary

Model merged with sita_mix as base.
It's a 2D professional model with thick lines and vivid colors.

caution

During the merger, Lori character didn't come out well due to a problem.

This model is not recommended for frequent drawing of Lori characters. But I think challenges are always right.

merge source

anything-v4.5

sita_mix

yaroArtstyleLora_v10

motomurabitoStyle_v1

agawaRyoStyleLORA_v2

pastelmixInspiredV5_v5

Settings

default CFG Scale : 6~8
default Sampler : DPM++ 2M Karras
default Steps : 25~30
Hires pix.
Upscaler : R-ESRGAN 4x+Anime6B

Denoising Strength : 0.4~0.6

Sample picture

t2i upscaled.
The 'Latent Couple' extension has been used for the couple illustration.

I hope the translator delivers my message well.
Good luck. ;)
